AN ACT
To authorize the conveyance of certain state property.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
Section 1. 1. The governor is hereby authorized and empowered to sell,
2 transfer, grant, convey, remise, release, and forever quitclaim all interest of the state of
3 Missouri in property located in Nodaway County, Missouri. The property to be
